💥Bulgarian Split Squat💥Get your photos/videos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting runningterritory.com/feature 👉🏼the link is in our bio: @RunningTerritory 
-
⁉️ Having trouble setting up your feet in the correct position for the Bulgarian Split Squat (Rear Foot Elevated Split Squat)?
-
😎 Don't worry! Here's a super simple tip you can start using today so that you never find yourself hopping around awkwardly and off balance again!
-
⁉️ Questions? Comments? Send me a message or leave a comment below ⬇️⬇️⬇️

📽 @dr.caleb.burgess
🎶 Montell Jordan - This Is How We Do It

node.text: Your solution to runners chafe!  www.trychafezone.com

by @nooch_13 🔥 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @RunningTerritory

Being able to load into the hips and glutes plays a major factor for many different sports, but often times some are unable to do so.

Here’s a few variations from my session with @spencem_4 that can not only allow the transfer of energy and power but can also allow the athlete to become more explosive.
